{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "萧秋水一行六人夜宿娄山会仙亭，遭'飞刀神魔'沙千灯与'铁骑神魔'阎鬼鬼偷袭。沙千灯飞刀灭烛，阎鬼鬼黑鞭暗袭唐方，众人奋力反击。六人连夜疾驰至黄果飞瀑，再遭'三绝剑魔'孔扬秦水底伏击，孔扬秦以白练分水剑穿马腹暗算唐方，被萧秋水推倒救下。邓玉函为救萧秋水挡下沙千灯飞刀，伤重身亡。萧秋水悲愤之下以浣花剑法'满天花雨'击伤沙千灯，邓玉函临死前拔刀反杀沙千灯。萧秋水再以'长虹贯日'剑招击杀孔扬秦，孔扬秦连人带剑坠入黄果飞瀑。此章痛失邓玉函，萧秋水立誓报仇。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家别乱，镇静应付，唐姑娘你……",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我没事。来的人是沙千灯。",
      "tone": "镇定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有阎鬼鬼！",
      "tone": "警觉",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然我们已给盯梢上，就星夜过贵州，入广西吧！",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！挡我者死！滚开者生！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那我们要不要去看看？去看看罗。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "我们正要绕白水河直上，再走盘江岸路渡乌江，此番正要一并去见识黄果飞瀑！",
      "tone": "豪爽",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对！那儿就是黄果飞瀑！好大！一千只犀牛在吼，一万个铜锣在同时敲打，十万只鸡蛋同时滑落，好大好大！",
      "tone": "兴奋",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "好了，老铁，你别形容了，你的形容是最煸线的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过那真的是惊人，真是鬼斧神工，我们上次在白天掠过，阳光清照，气氛绝胜，逼遭数十丈彩幻迷蒙一片，你看，这镇上还距离黄果飞瀑那么远，但已水气弥空了。",
      "tone": "赞叹",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出来！",
      "tone": "怒喝",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "老大，你——！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要乱，还有强敌伺伏！",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心那灯笼！他就是'红灯魅'、'飞刀神魔'沙千灯！",
      "tone": "警示",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "text": "三绝剑魔？孔扬秦？！",
      "tone": "警觉",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "孔扬秦",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我的剑是在水底练成的，叫做'白练分水剑'，这是三绝中其中一绝。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "text": "好剑。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "text": "可惜。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "孔扬秦",
      "listener": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "text": "可惜什么？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "text": "可惜人是极卑下的人。",
      "tone": "鄙夷",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "text": "凭一代剑术宗师还施这种卑鄙的暗算，失敬得很！",
      "tone": "讥讽",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "text": "简直不配使这柄剑。",
      "tone": "傲然",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "孔扬秦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来如此！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "text": "什么如此？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "孔扬秦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人有五张口，骂架是可以，吃饭也行，打起来嘛……除非是狗咬狗！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "孔扬秦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没料到女孩子有两张口……你们这几个男孩子也有！",
      "tone": "下流",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "text": "孔扬秦，亏你还是武林名宿，居然讲出这种话，你……！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "孔扬秦",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "你什么！反正你们已活不过今天晚上，我讲的话，又有谁知道，哈哈哈哈……不过我对你嘛，就可以温柔一些——",
      "tone": "淫邪",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看剑！",
      "tone": "怒喝",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_yang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "孔扬秦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "浣花剑？",
      "tone": "哼声",
      "chapter": 16
    }
  ],
